T1  - Intangible assets, entry strategies, and venture success in industrial markets
AU  - Williams, Mary L.
AU  - Tsai, Ming-Hone
AU  - Day, Diana
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 6
IS  - 5
SP  - 315
EP  - 333
PY  - 1991
