T1  - Evaluating the costs of raising capital through an initial public offering
AU  - Aggarwal, Reena
AU  - Rivoli, Pietra
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 6
IS  - 5
SP  - 351
EP  - 361
PY  - 1991
DA  - 1991/09/01/
